title: Sec 8 approved - 3 bed / 1 bath
posting_body: ['Section 8 approved.', ' 3 bed / 1 bath unit located on the 2nd floor of a 4-plex.', 'This unit has access to a large outdoor deck.', ' Off street parking lot - each tenant is allowed 1 parking space only.', 'Central heat and air.', 'On-site, coin operated laundry.', ' Pets are permitted with pre-approval and a one-time, non-refundable fee of $300.00.', 'Security deposit is $2250.00 which includes a non-refundable cleaning fee of $250.00.', 'Rent is $1750.00 per month.', 'Application fee is $100.00 per adult.', ' Landlord pays water, trash, septic.', ' Tenant pays gas and electric.', ' Unit is available October 1, 2022.', ' 1 year lease required.', 'Absolutely no smoking in unit or in building.', ' Smoking inside the unit will result in automatic loss of security deposit.']
